CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 22, 1958, pg. 23 reads: "Seek Title - Allegheny High School is expected to go all out in quest of the city high school championship against Westinghouse High School Friday night. Allegheny's starting line-up in shown above.  Left to right, front row: Larry Pridgen, end; Vic Mamich, tackle; Gerald Roper, guard; Bill Hamilton, center; Frank Rodrigues, guard; William Lukitsch, tackle, and Erble Moore, end.  Back row: Otis Wesley, right half; Darrell Bryant, quarterback; Head Coach Bruce Allen, Anthony Tuminello, halfback, and Bernie Stein, left halfback.  -Harris Photo."
